## 1. Input Contract
- Required:
  - `doc_type`: `order_draft | submit_draft | letter_draft`
  - `stage2_facts`: non-empty list
  - `incoming_level`: `from_direct_superior | from_superior | from_peer | from_subordinate | general`
- Optional:
