  - subsequent occurrences use short alias (`?ж®ү?зҳЈ?..?иі№оҪ…?/?оөЈж»ҝ or `?и¬ҚжёӣиҝӨ?пҺҗп”Ҙ?и¬Қе Ҡйј“...?иІ•?
- MUST remove non-owner obligations from `??????` and `?иҹЎпҺҠ?`.
  - example forbidden clause: `???????оөЈйјҺ??зҚў?????????..`
  - keep only current unit-owned actions.
- MUST evaluate `?еҡ—??з¶ңз«Ҙ?` and `?и¬•оӨў??з¶ңз«Ҙ?` in the same ranking pool.
- MUST NOT treat `?еҡ—??з¶ңз«Ҙ?` as unconditional keep (except fixed quote and research-opinion constraints).
- SHOULD keep each explain point concise and actionable.

